                <head ana="#head_untitled-missing-head-in-printed-volume">[Untitled]</head>
                <note rend="inline" type="source">[Telegram.—Sent June 22, at 7 o’clock p.
                    m.]</note>
                <note rend="inline" type="source">[For the Secretary of State, Washington.]</note>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-06-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 22</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="italic">To the American consul, Queenstown, Cork:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>I am authorized to say that orders will be given to the captain general of Cuba
                    to deliver the Stonewall to the government of the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HORATIO J. PERRY.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
